Cryptocoin.se's BTC-e watcher
C# tool to monitor and notify about currency changes at btc-e.com.

Supported:
BTC / USD
LTC / BTC
LTC / USD

- Sound notification on increasing and/or decreasing price 
- Email notifications at custom high/low limits

Version: 1.0

This project has two dependencies:
1. BtceApi		https://github.com/DmT021/BtceApi
2. Newtonsoft.Json	https://github.com/JamesNK/Newtonsoft.Json

Created by cryptocoin.se
